THE ROLE
Expand all
The Role
An exciting opportunity has become available for a new role here in Dubai for a PA to a CEO and Deputy CEO
Duties:
- Diary Management for both the CEO and Deputy CEO
- CEO travels frequently so there will be lots of arranging
- Booking flights, hotels, travel
- Preparing agendas
- Managing the office approx. 20 - 30 people
- Sitting in on meetings taking minutes in meetings
- Typing correspondence responding to emails
- Preparing documents and presentations
- Liaising with departments as requested
- The candidate must be flexible and able to work in busy business environment
- Translation Arabic in to English
REQUIREMENTS
Requirements
- Arabic required with excellent English, preferably Lebanese
- Min 5 years experience
- Flexible on working hours
- Well presented, professional
- Good English Grammar and communication
- UAE experience advantageous but not essential but professional service industry experience
Salary & Benefits
15-20,000 AED (dep exp)
- Medical
- Annual Flight
- Parking
